<item>
            <title>[LU-607] port bz24419 (ldlm namespace lock contention during oom)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-607</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While running a regression test:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2011-01-20 19:14:30&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;c0-0c0s5n0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;Kernel panic - not syncing: oom_kill_process killing invalid app&lt;br/&gt;
